title: Hey! I'm in your walls!
author: DillyzThe1
text:
Heyo!
So I see you've either managed to compile this or grab a dev build.
That's interesting! Welcome to the program!
Here, you can set up mods in under 2 minutes to play.

Hit the 'mods' button, click install anywhere, and launch the game!
Of course, don't forget to install the client first.
